import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'
import EmployeeRegistrationForm from '../employee/EmployeeRegistrationForm'
import EmployeeAddPage from '../employee/EmployeeAddPage'
import CustomerAddPage from '../customer/CustomerAddPage'

import Header from '../header/Header'


const GeneralRouter =()=>{
    return(
        <Router>
            <Switch>

                <Route exact path= "/employee/add" component = {EmployeeAddPage}/>
                <Route exact path="/employee/list" component={EmployeeAddPage}/>
                <Route exact path= "/customer/add" component = {CustomerAddPage}/>
                <Route exact path= "/materials/add" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>
                <Route exact path= "/materials/list" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>
                <Route exact path= "/customers/list" component = {EmployeeRegistrationForm}/>

                <Route exact path= "/" component = {Header}/>

            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}
export default GeneralRouter
